frames.caption: An imposing figure stands in a mystical forest under a bright full moon. The figure, adorned in elaborate robes and a golden crown, holds a glowing staff that emits fiery sparks. The surrounding trees and night sky create an enchanting atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a magical setting in a forest at night, illuminated by the moon and the fiery glow of a staff. The central figure appears to be a wizard or sorcerer, exuding an aura of power and mystery.

frames.caption: An elderly figure in ornate robes stands in a mystical forest under a bright full moon. He holds a staff topped with a glowing orb, surrounded by small flames on the ground. The scene is illuminated by both the moonlight and the fiery glow of the staff.
frames.description: The scene depicts a magical setting in a forest at night, where an enigmatic figure appears to be performing a ritual or spell. The atmosphere is mystical and serene, with a sense of ancient wisdom and power.
